  "title": "Export Sales Coordinator [Sales Support | West]",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1395144]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Handle sales enquiries, prepare quotations, and coordinate order consolidation</li><li>Process customer orders promptly and ensure accurate invoicing</li><li>Prepare and organize export shipping documents, including Bill of Lading, packing list, certificates, and insurance documents</li><li>Provide timely updates on cargo arrival and departure schedules to stakeholders</li><li>Liaise with the Logistics Department on delivery schedules and inventory matters</li><li>Ensure invoices from external service providers are submitted promptly for processing</li><li>Assist in warranty and insurance claim processing</li><li>Maintain accurate records of all sales and shipping documentation</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum Diploma or equivalent qualification</strong></li><li><strong>At least 1 year of experience in handling export shipping documents, such as Bill of Lading, packing list, and certificate of origin</strong></li><li>Meticulous, detail-oriented, and organized</li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Felicia Chiam Kar Min<br />EA Personnel Reg. No.: R25152370<br />EA Licence No.: 07C5771 </p>",
